trans-unit.target: Ger stöd för designtid för <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroller.

trans-unit.source: EditorPartDesigner is a public implementation of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.PartDesigner> base class for the purpose of rendering <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls at design time.
trans-unit.target: EditorPartDesigner är en offentlig implementering av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.PartDesigner>basklassen för återgivning <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller vid designtillfället.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.PartDesigner>

trans-unit.source: It adds the capability of carrying zone information from the associated control into design view, but does not otherwise change the functionality of the parent control.
trans-unit.target: Det lägger till möjligheten att genomföra zoninformationen från den associerade kontrollen i designvyn, men har inte annars ändra funktionerna i den överordnade kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: As with other control designers, you can change the design-time rendering of custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart> controls by inheriting from EditorPartDesigner and overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Som med andra kontrollen designers, du kan ändra designläge återgivning av anpassade <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>kontroller genom arv från EditorPartDesigner och åsidosätta den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart>

trans-unit.source: If you want to override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A> method, be sure to include the base implementation so as to retain zone information.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill åsidosätta den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A>metod, se till att ta den grundläggande implementeringen så att zoninformation.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner.CreateViewControl%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPartDesigner"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Creates a copy of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control to render at design time.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en kopia av den associerade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontrollen ska renderas i designläge.

trans-unit.source: This method is overridden to copy zone information to the view control.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden åsidosätts för att kopiera zoninformation till view-kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: A copy of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: En kopia av den associerade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Verifies that the control resides in a zone of type <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase"></xref>, and then gets the markup that is used to represent the control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Verifierar att kontrollen finns i en zon av typen <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase"> </xref>, och sedan hämtar koden som används för att representera kontrollen i designläge.

trans-unit.source: The markup that is used to represent the control at design time, or error markup if the control does not reside in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Den kod som används för att representera kontrollen i designläge eller fel markup om kontrollen inte finns i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorZoneBase"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Binds the designer to the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Binder designern till den associerade <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"> </xref> kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.EditorPart"></xref> control associated with the designer.
